{"tid":458971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<有無觸犯國歌法？>中韓足球大戰  中國球迷狂噓南韓國歌","createTime":"2017-11-05T11:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T14:12:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"022e5945343eca8b774ad991fe11818cba8acad3","tid":458971,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"中韓足球大戰　陸球迷狂噓南韓國歌<br />\n<br />\n2017/03/23 21:19<br />\n<br />\n中國國家隊今晚在湖南長沙迎戰南韓隊，進行2018俄羅斯世界盃的外圍賽。賽事開始奏南韓國歌時，場內的中國球迷不斷發出噓聲和吹哨聲。微博網友貼文說「剛剛奏韓國國歌時，全場都在噓和吹哨兒！」不少網友都大罵當地球迷：「韓國國歌一片噓聲，長沙智障還是多！」「長沙這麼噓&hellip;&hellip;到底是敏感時期&hellip;&hellip;」「這個國的民族自豪就是這樣培養起來的，shame on you！」<br />\n<br />\n「在其他國家奏國歌的時候連基本的尊重都沒有嗎？​」「奏韓國國歌，噓聲，吼聲四起，已經輸了，丟人啊！」「這麼噓別人的國歌，還喊『棒子』，太丟人了，賽後估計還得被罰！」比賽奏國歌時發出噓聲是不當行為，2015中港大戰，有香港球迷噓國歌，國際足協裁定足總違反了《國際足協紀律章程第67條1及3節》，罰款7.7萬元港幣。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170323/1083078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170323%2F1083078%2F&d=fgHembKfD7570e%2FuwPqsh3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5f383455\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170323%2F1083078%2F&h=17e08cb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170323/1083078/</a>"},{"pid":"e0a56a5c7d1668e35e7c80eff1f65092a0c0b767","tid":458971,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085324b9cc6d36a6eb3b0794453309d34f34a176","tid":458971,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68347570814f62b2c59c60e386bc279cad5f4b2e","tid":458971,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"中國球迷噓對手國歌"},{"pid":"68d712377f1998885d4cbc12384e23f05ed12f7b","tid":45